**Delete these files/directories:**
- `next.config.ts`
- `next-env.d.ts`
- `src/app/` (entire directory â€” layout.tsx, page.tsx, globals.css, api/)
- `prisma/` (entire directory â€” schema.prisma)
- `src/lib/db.ts` (Prisma singleton)
- `db/` (SQLite database file)
- `Caddyfile`
- `.zscripts/`
- `examples/`
- `mini-services/`
- `download/`
- `dev.log`
- `tool-results/`
- `bun.lock`
- `components.json` (will regenerate with Vite-compatible config)
- `.env` (contains Prisma SQLite URL â€” will replace)
- `eslint.config.mjs` (Next.js-specific config â€” will replace)

