## Step 7: Convert API layer (mock client â†’ Axios + MSW)

- **`src/api/client.ts`** â€” Axios instance with `baseURL: import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL`, interceptors for token attachment and 401 refresh.
- **`src/api/auth.ts`** â€” Auth API functions (login, register, etc.) using the Axios client.
- **`src/api/students.ts`** â€” Student API functions.
- **`src/api/courses.ts`** â€” Course API functions.
- **`src/api/performance.ts`** â€” Grade/GPA API functions.
- **`src/api/ai.ts`** â€” AI module API functions.
- **`src/api/admin.ts`** â€” Admin API functions.
- **`src/api/public.ts`** â€” Public site API functions.
- **`src/api/handlers.ts`** â€” MSW handlers matching `context/api-reference.md` shapes, using the existing mock data.
- **`src/api/types.ts`** â€” Keep existing types, remove `AppRoute` (moves to routes/).
- **`src/api/mock-data.ts`** â€” Keep existing mock data.
- Remove `src/lib/db.ts` (Prisma).

