## Step 8: Update all component imports

Every component that imports from `@/contexts/router-context` needs to switch to `react-router-dom`:
- `useRouter()` â†’ `useNavigate()` + `useLocation()` + `useParams()`
- `navigate('route-name')` â†’ `navigate('/path')`
- `currentRoute` â†’ `useLocation().pathname`

Every component that imports from `next-themes` needs to switch to `@/contexts/theme-context`.

Remove all `'use client'` directives (they're Next.js RSC markers, meaningless in Vite).

